---
title: Creamy Indian Chickpea Tacos with Pickled Onion & Roasted Cashews
description: These tacos hit all the right marks – they are full with pops of crunchy cucumber, creamy spiced chickpeas, crispy leaves and a
fresh hint of mint. Not to mention they are high in fibre and protein. It’s a winner, winner veggie dinner!
